{"tid":1671271,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【長期支援】我 哋 想 攪 一 個 教 育 基 金 幫 義 士","createTime":"2019-10-23T11:13:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T16:12:56.000Z","uid":36164,"like":38,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"6f2233451fa4ed24cc82af74beb6775ab5ce5909","tid":1671271,"uid":36164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T11:13:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">義士唔係Condom, <br />\n我哋知好多人已經為義士做咗好多嘢<br />\n例如義務律師團隊,私家醫生,家長接送,甚至係食飯都好多人幫手<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n不過我哋覺得，<br />\n學業支援方面只得補習服務未夠。<br />\n我地和理非唔想義士因為香港而犧牲前途，<br />\n就算餐餐捱麵包都要供佢哋去外國讀大學！<br />\n所以我哋幾個人有個諗法，<br />\n就係想攪個教育基金做長遠既供書教學。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n集思廣益！<br />\n唔知大家對教育基金呢個idea有咩意見？<br />\n你覺得有無咩地方需要特別小心注意？<br />\n<br />\n好希望大家可以幫手諗吓 <br />\n唔該晒咁多位巴絲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（如果已經有手足籌備緊或者攪咗，<br />\n請告知，我哋唔會另起爐灶，<br />\n反而想睇下有無嘢我哋可以幫手。）"},{"pid":"6a8d7ed6baa8e6d2bf2cc85d77d905361593b592","tid":1671271,"uid":160075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T11:14:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e112eee638c62c81ec950c188d1eccfb506d3d3f","tid":1671271,"uid":322141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T11:14:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2039e5d15d0fd0335cb446197f8159be476de456","tid":1671271,"uid":136113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T11:15:10.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"7730e77b29cf10d9dc96fe74071ad74f2670bf68","tid":1671271,"uid":36164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T11:49:13.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"671ab8ee719c94cf71b951bf39c2e03d0a18da52","tid":1671271,"uid":177944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T12:18:16.000Z","msg":"Pish <img s